enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve modifying the allowed attributes for a tag, making them complementary for setting up test scenarios.
Removing tags can indirectly affect the attributes allowed for those tags, which is relevant for testing attribute removal.
The method 'isSafeAttribute' checks if an attribute is allowed, which is directly related to the removal of attributes in 'removeAttributes'.
Enforced attributes can influence the behavior of attribute removal, making it necessary to test their interaction.
